{"author":"Joe Oakhart","author_email":"joeoakhart+bot@navapbc.com","author_id":"594c-9dcf-5ad6-4e6d","author_sig":"{\"payload\": \"\", \"payloadType\": \"application/vnd.rebar.authorship.v1+json\", \"signatures\": [{\"keyid\": \"594c-9dcf-5ad6-4e6d\", \"sig\": \"\"}]}","data":{"content_hash":"e705f2d98820755a593f414b37768b962b8627f7b015755a104221e56f839af7","digest":{"component_or_area":"identity enforcement / authorship verification gate","key_entities":["identity.enforce_since","identity.require_authenticated","REBAR_IDENTITY_ENFORCE_SINCE","--since","src/rebar/_commands/verify_authorship.py","src/rebar/_config_schema.py","_is_enforced","tests/unit/test_identity_enforce_since_grandfather.py","rebar verify-identity --all --require-authenticated --since","git merge-base --is-ancestor","rebar.toml","grandfathered"],"problem_keywords":["grandfathering","enforcement boundary","write-signing","identity authentication","regression test","pre-flip events","anchor commit","fail-closed gate"],"propositions":["The grandfathering check must enforce authorship only for events whose introducing commit is the enforce_since anchor or a descendant, treating strict ancestors as grandfathered.","The enforcement-boundary anchor must be an existing tickets-branch commit that every pre-signing unsigned event strictly precedes, chosen after write-signing is confirmed live across all writers.","A regression test must drive the boundary via the identity.enforce_since config/env path and assert per-event grandfathered flags in a mixed store where pre-boundary unsigned events pass and post-boundary unsigned/forged events fail.","This story decides and records the anchor SHA and rationale but does not write enforce_since or flip require_authenticated, leaving rebar.toml unmodified.","Verification via 'verify-identity --all --require-authenticated --since <anchor>' must exit 0 with zero enforced-unverified events."]},"digest_hash_version":1,"model":"claude-opus-4-8","schema":"ticket_digest_v1"},"env_id":"ade0f2ef-51cc-45a2-bb97-c09846cd3df5","event_type":"TICKET_DIGEST","timestamp":1784263252943133001,"uuid":"94a6132b-4aaa-41f4-b656-71b51ee3a926"}